Message.MsgText: UNEXPECTED_TOP_ELEMENT_IN_RES_REF=CWSAN1000W: When parsing Blueprint xml, the parser ignored an unknown top-level element {0} in the namespace http://www.ibm.com/appserver/schemas/8.0/blueprint/resourcereference.
Message.Explanation: The top-level element in the resource reference namespace must be resource-reference.
Message.UserResponse: Check the Blueprint xml for possible misspellings, or remove the incorrect element.
